技工都係，9下9下咁，想搵人幫手都冇人理你</blockquote><br />\n做管理果班要有良好溝通先夾到野，做前線果班又係要溝通先做到野，除左部份室內裝修，地盤真係無乜野可以一條友做晒</blockquote><br />\n工程＝毒撚依個諗法真係害死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁我真係唔知咩叫毒撚喇，工作上講幾句野都唔得，咁無工岩你做，無一份工唔使同人溝通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ebf1734095fd90759f47a179f27795cd378d431","tid":346241,"uid":119695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T00:42:29.000Z","msg":"倒垃圾，掃街"},{"pid":"e5dca37187c340789f9bcdcc5ecbeef4a08dccfd","tid":346241,"uid":56682,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T00:46:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>電競選手</blockquote><br />\n應對技巧，要同觀眾同主持人溝通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec25739b60535bf83ca1ba9e950ba21523057c3e","tid":346241,"uid":81569,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T00:51:18.000Z","msg":"面對現實啦，係商業化既社會<br />\n冇錢/樣衰既毒撚根本冇存在價值"},{"pid":"aa560149ce6fdad0be84cae10abb9a240f5d42c2","tid":346241,"uid":49157,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T00:54:23.000Z","msg":"點解唔諗點改變唔做毒撚 而係諗應該揀咩工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d61ebb4c045c076bc1b6e46f6b5627dee26dd698","tid":346241,"uid":123605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T00:55:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解唔諗點改變唔做毒撚 而係諗應該揀咩工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18df85f58cbfb4a2fbfd5e81099bbfc5a744cf65","tid":346241,"uid":50870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T01:22:26.000Z","msg":"點解樓主已經講左it仲有咁多人跳出黎講it工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gi